Class computorCSVReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • gradecomputor.computorCSVReader

  • public class computorCSVReader
extends java.lang.Object
    This Class responsible for reading the CSV (Comma-Separated Values) file and obtain the relevant information for the display and grade judgment.

      • parseSection

        private java.lang.String parseSection(java.lang.String s)
        A hack to obtain the section unique from the CSV file. The field is usually written in the form "PHY102M(55345)" and with the extraction it results in "55345".
        Parameters:
        s - String to be parsed.
        Returns:
        unique The unique string of the section.
        Since:
        version 0.10

      • setCSVInfo

        private void setCSVInfo()
        This is "hand-written" method which is to be modified from the source (i.e. here).
